# Portfolio: Personal Website for Himanshu Shrivastava

## Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 16 (App Router, `output: 'export'` — static only)
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 (CSS-first `@theme` config in `app/globals.css`)
- **Animation**: Framer Motion
- **Blog**: MDX via `next-mdx-remote/rsc` + `gray-matter`
- **Testing**: Vitest + React Testing Library (100% coverage enforced)
- **Deploy**: GitHub Pages via GitHub Actions

## Key Commands
```bash
npm run dev           # Dev server
npm run build         # Static export → out/
npm run lint          # ESLint
npm run type-check    # tsc --noEmit
npm run test          # Vitest watch
npm run test:coverage # Enforce 100% coverage
```

## Architecture Constraints
- NO server-side features: no API routes, no getServerSideProps, no middleware
- `next/image` unoptimized (required for static export)
- Resume data ONLY from `lib/constants.ts`
- Blog posts ONLY in `content/blog/*.mdx`
- Every component must have a corresponding test

> See `AGENTS.md` for the full coding conventions guide.
